result.name: 喜茶HEYTEA (Shatin)

reviews.text: Brown sugar milk tea and Golden Jade Cheezo with boba was great. Crowded, as expected from other reviews. Ordering doesn't take too long but orders can take a while to make. Worth the wait though!
I tried the famous very grape cheezo and it is really cheeze-zy with lots of grapes fruit. Expect a long queue plus half an hour of waiting time after buying a ticket though.

I am a repeat customer of HeyTea because of its consistent quality. I’ve tried 四季春 with less sweet. The combination of cheese and tea is perfect. 

As for wait time, it’s about 15 mins in a Saturday afternoon.

This is my favorite place for bubble tea. Before I needed to go to Shenzhen to have this one. They finally open in Hong Kong, the product quality is very good, all very nice. The only bad thing about this place is the queue line. Take too much time to order and to receive your drinks. If you have time or you see this place without customers you must try it.
Generally good but a bit pricy and long waiting time

reviews.text: Great place for shopping with lots of shops and restaurants. Phase III is currently under renovation but surprisingly, it provides clear directory to guide you to your destination. However, the mall is extremely busy, packed with tourists and locals. Recommend to go on weekday.

parkview restaurant is good. the all day breakfast is good and the price is reasonable. the restaurant provide good food and service. the pumpkin cream soup and English sausage is delicious but the bacon is too salty!!🤗🤔
Consists of high end fashion shops. You can find maja, Sandro, Zara, coach, longchamp those kind of shop. They also have a snoopy land right next to it. Good to kill time.
Very good mall with lots of good brands. Have very good promotional offers for luxury skin care brands. Purchased Estee lauder skin care set at more than half off the price
Big Shopping centre very good . Many BIg shop standby here. Transport famlier and convenient.

result.name: 喜茶

reviews.text:
今日喺新城市廣場食完飯後，有一個朋友提議去飲喜茶，我本身有啲抗拒，因為每逢星期六日都見到佢排晒長龍，打晒蛇餅，睇見都驚😑😑但個朋友話好好飲，於是我去碰下運氣。點知去到竟然無咩人排隊咋，可能因為9點半，太夜啦

我哋分別叫咗一杯芝芝莓果同芝士金鳳茶王

芝芝莓果係藍莓加草莓，再加芝士奶蓋
呢杯顏色粉白色，配埋白色嘅奶蓋，好夢幻
先用飲管飲一啖，菓味好香。之後再飲一啖連奶蓋，奶蓋嘅鹹香冇得彈，不過加埋果香味道就有啲濃

芝士金鳳茶王係茶加芝士奶蓋
呢杯茶色金黃色好特別，配上厚厚嘅奶蓋
同樣，先用飲管飲一啖，入口茶香濃，潤滑不澀口，尾韻清香厚實，餘韻甚至能感覺到喉嚨都留有茶的餘香味，有別於常見的茉莉，帶有難以言喻的清爽花香。之後再飲一啖連奶蓋，茶嘅清香加上奶蓋嘅鹹香……嘩！簡直絕配呀🙀🙀🙀我覺得比芝芝莓果更好飲啊
成50蚊杯茶好很貴，不過又真係好飲既，可惜要等成半小時

平日下午5時購買的人不多不用排長隊，5分鐘便可購買，10分鐘可取飲品
芝芝桃桃有鮮桃粒茶香好味

可以直接用手機下單，到的時候再過去店內就行，很方便。。
平常聽大家說這家不錯，這次就買了芝士金鳳茶王來嘗嘗。。
手機下單後，手機顯示還有9+個才到我，還以為要等很久，大概十多分鐘後手機就提示可以到店內拿取。。
到手後，先嘗嘗上層的芝士奶蓋，有點油油的感覺，個人來講不太喜愛，芝士味是不錯啦，到下面的茶，茶味不太重。。。下次會考慮試水果類的

環境大，設計靚，有很多座位。
早上較少人，價錢較為高
員工服務態度還好
最喜歡芝芝莓果、芝芝芒芒、芝芝桃桃
